Dear Partner,


As part of our continuous efforts to improve our digital offerings, we are excited to announce the BETA launch of the STOCH Platform, (Saudi Content Hub) the first nation-wide platform where finding curated content related to Saudi Arabia is made easy and publicly accessible.


As a partner, you are playing a crucial role in the continued success of the platform as we expand its use cases and add new features. STOCH currently allows you to search and download images and videos, as well as upload and tag new ones. You can also utilize the smart recommendations capabilities built into the platform.


As we transition away from the current asset bank, we are inviting you to join and start experiencing the future of smart content today! Simply follow the steps below:


  1. Click on this link - link will be valid for 7 days only
  2. Reset your password
  3. Navigate to STOCH homepage
  4. Click the ‘Sign-In’ button
  5. Use your STA email and the new password you just created
  6. Enjoy STOCH
